  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Welcome to Toon Toon Racing!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319260/extras/64b6f1a738ad17fb0cf4c036705c38dd.poster.avif?t=1767982231\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319260/extras/64b6f1a738ad17fb0cf4c036705c38dd.webm?t=1767982231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319260/extras/64b6f1a738ad17fb0cf4c036705c38dd.mp4?t=1767982231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Master challenging tracks with SIMCADE mechanics that strike a perfect balance between realism and arcade fun. Toon Toon Racing is easy to learn, but difficult to master, offering accessible yet challenging gameplay for those looking for a true racing experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Race in different scenarios!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319260/extras/e1dd46434177b24ff961b578ac8c058e.poster.avif?t=1767982231\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319260/extras/e1dd46434177b24ff961b578ac8c058e.webm?t=1767982231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319260/extras/e1dd46434177b24ff961b578ac8c058e.mp4?t=1767982231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Whether it's the thrilling corners or the thrilling straights, every race is an opportunity to stand out and win in style. Choose your car, feel the adrenaline and get ready to experience the most exciting race of your life!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Explore our garage!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319260/extras/70aeda78c43889de20e6d78806c52aaf.poster.avif?t=1767982231\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319260/extras/70aeda78c43889de20e6d78806c52aaf.webm?t=1767982231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319260/extras/70aeda78c43889de20e6d78806c52aaf.mp4?t=1767982231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Toon Toon Racing offers a garage full of incredible vehicles for you to choose from! From nimble classics to rugged, super-fast machines, each car has its own personality and driving style, ready to stand out on the game's vibrant tracks.  <br> <br><strong><i>Join our community on Discord!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319260/extras/910076392a195ce2c6b29242cfed0a74.avif?t=1767982231\" width=616 height=338 /></span>Want to stay up to date with the latest Toon Toon Racing news? Exchange driving tips, share your achievements, or even suggest new ideas for the game? Our community is waiting for you!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Welcome to Toon Toon Racing!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319260/extras/64b6f1a738ad17fb0cf4c036705c38dd.poster.avif?t=1767982231\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319260/extras/64b6f1a738ad17fb0cf4c036705c38dd.webm?t=1767982231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319260/extras/64b6f1a738ad17fb0cf4c036705c38dd.mp4?t=1767982231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Master challenging tracks with SIMCADE mechanics that strike a perfect balance between realism and arcade fun. Toon Toon Racing is easy to learn, but difficult to master, offering accessible yet challenging gameplay for those looking for a true racing experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Race in different scenarios!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319260/extras/e1dd46434177b24ff961b578ac8c058e.poster.avif?t=1767982231\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319260/extras/e1dd46434177b24ff961b578ac8c058e.webm?t=1767982231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319260/extras/e1dd46434177b24ff961b578ac8c058e.mp4?t=1767982231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Whether it's the thrilling corners or the thrilling straights, every race is an opportunity to stand out and win in style. Choose your car, feel the adrenaline and get ready to experience the most exciting race of your life!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Explore our garage!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319260/extras/70aeda78c43889de20e6d78806c52aaf.poster.avif?t=1767982231\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319260/extras/70aeda78c43889de20e6d78806c52aaf.webm?t=1767982231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319260/extras/70aeda78c43889de20e6d78806c52aaf.mp4?t=1767982231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Toon Toon Racing offers a garage full of incredible vehicles for you to choose from! From nimble classics to rugged, super-fast machines, each car has its own personality and driving style, ready to stand out on the game's vibrant tracks.  <br> <br><strong><i>Join our community on Discord!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319260/extras/910076392a195ce2c6b29242cfed0a74.avif?t=1767982231\" width=616 height=338 /></span>Want to stay up to date with the latest Toon Toon Racing news? Exchange driving tips, share your achievements, or even suggest new ideas for the game? Our community is waiting for you!</p>",
